<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 16:08:12 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“医生想做的第一件事就是减轻某人的痛苦。在加沙，这是不可能的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-first-thing-a-doctor-wants-to-do-is-ease-someones-pain-in-gaza-thats-impossible/0000018d-b786-dbbd-a5dd-f7c7b0400000</link><description>“加沙的灾难比我过去见过的任何灾难都要严重，”在代尔巴拉赫急诊室做志愿者的医生詹姆斯·史密斯博士在接受《国土报》采访时说道。他补充说，间接发病率的规模只有在未来才会变得清晰</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 15:34:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-02-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-first-thing-a-doctor-wants-to-do-is-ease-someones-pain-in-gaza-thats-impossible/0000018d-b786-dbbd-a5dd-f7c7b0400000</guid></item><item><title>前往暴行地点的旅游揭露了以色列人告诉自己的谎言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/tourism-to-atrocity-sites-exposes-the-lie-israelis-tell-themselves/0000018d-b542-d8ee-a5cf-b7de48250000</link><description>撒玛利亚一日游和访问南部战区之间存在联系：否认以色列实际面临的现实</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 04:51:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/tourism-to-atrocity-sites-exposes-the-lie-israelis-tell-themselves/0000018d-b542-d8ee-a5cf-b7de48250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列科学家在实验室培育睾丸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-02-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-israeli-scientist-who-is-growing-testicles-in-a-lab/0000018d-b448-d8ee-a5cf-b7dc9a340000</link><description>尼赞·戈南 (Nitzan Gonen) 博士对人们对她的工作的嘲笑并不陌生，但她对人造睾丸将能够帮助不育男性持谨慎乐观的态度</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 04:09:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-02-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-israeli-scientist-who-is-growing-testicles-in-a-lab/0000018d-b448-d8ee-a5cf-b7dc9a340000</guid></item><item><title>官员表示，哈马斯将冻结人质/停火谈判，直到人道主义援助进入加沙北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article-live/new-york-times-reports-israel-responsible-for-attacks-on-two-iranian-pipelines/0000018d-b4ce-d8ee-a5cf-b7de87920000</link><description>以色列国防军部队在加沙纳赛尔医院院落逮捕了 100 名恐怖分子嫌疑人 ■ 以色列军队称，他们在一夜之间袭击了叙利亚境内的发射场、阿萨德军队的武器库 ■ 法国马克龙表示，巴勒斯坦国“不再是禁忌”</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 02:25:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article-live/new-york-times-reports-israel-responsible-for-attacks-on-two-iranian-pipelines/0000018d-b4ce-d8ee-a5cf-b7de87920000</guid></item><item><title>纽约时报：以色列是伊朗主要天然气管道袭击的幕后黑手</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/new-york-times-israel-is-behind-attacks-on-main-iranian-gas-pipelines/0000018d-b468-d8ee-a5cf-b7fc74b40000</link><description>据接受《纽约时报》采访的消息人士透露，所谓的以色列袭击扰乱了伊朗几个省份的供热和烹饪燃气供应。能源专家补充说，袭击导致伊朗日天然气产量减少约 15%</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 00:48:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article/new-york-times-israel-is-behind-attacks-on-main-iranian-gas-pipelines/0000018d-b468-d8ee-a5cf-b7fc74b40000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦青少年正在写遗嘱，这是有充分理由的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-02-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/palestinian-teens-are-writing-wills-and-for-a-good-reason/0000018d-ad78-d070-a7fd-ff7c855c0000</link><description>当高中生阿卜杜勒·拉赫曼·哈马德 (Abdel Rahman Hamad) 从学校步行回家时，一名以色列士兵向他的腹部开枪，导致他死亡。他去世后，他半年前写给家人的一封信出现了。他是西岸许多正在写遗嘱的青少年之一</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 23:37:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-02-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/palestinian-teens-are-writing-wills-and-for-a-good-reason/0000018d-ad78-d070-a7fd-ff7c855c0000</guid></item><item><title>“没有游客，也没有犹太人”：战争导致拿撒勒遭遇悲惨命运</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/no-tourists-and-no-jews-a-sad-fate-has-befallen-nazareth-due-to-the-war/0000018d-ae03-d070-a7fd-fe27c73f0000</link><description>战争、恐惧和惩罚以色列阿拉伯人的呼声已经使拿撒勒的街道空无一人。没有以色列或外国游客来访，当地居民也没有心情外出就餐。酒店和餐馆老板剩下的就是希望有更好的时光</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 23:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/no-tourists-and-no-jews-a-sad-fate-has-befallen-nazareth-due-to-the-war/0000018d-ae03-d070-a7fd-fe27c73f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列称超过 30 名驻加沙的联合国援助人员参与了 10 月 7 日哈马斯的袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-says-over-30-un-aid-workers-in-gaza-participated-in-hamas-attacks-on-october-7/0000018d-b39b-dc8c-a3df-f3bf65be0000</link><description>以色列国防部长约阿夫·加兰特向记者展示了情报，据称该情报表明近东救济工程处员工参与了劫持平民和士兵的人质事件</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 20:48:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-says-over-30-un-aid-workers-in-gaza-participated-in-hamas-attacks-on-october-7/0000018d-b39b-dc8c-a3df-f3bf65be0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院拒绝南非要求采取紧急措施保护拉法免受以色列进攻的请求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/icj-rejects-request-for-urgent-measures-to-shield-rafah-from-israeli-offensive/0000018d-b39b-dfc6-abed-f79fb8250000</link><description>法院强调，迫切需要执行上个月种族灭绝案件裁决中概述的临时措施，这些措施适用于包括拉法在内的整个加沙地带，而无需采取额外措施</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 20:47:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/icj-rejects-request-for-urgent-measures-to-shield-rafah-from-israeli-offensive/0000018d-b39b-dfc6-abed-f79fb8250000</guid></item><item><title>只有提前选举才能使以色列免遭毁灭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/only-an-early-election-can-save-israel-from-ruin/0000018d-b2e4-dc8c-a3df-f2f5d03b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 18:14:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/only-an-early-election-can-save-israel-from-ruin/0000018d-b2e4-dc8c-a3df-f2f5d03b0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 133 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-133/0000018d-b2ff-d11b-af9d-b7ffaa130000</link><description>以色列南部恐怖袭击造成两人死亡、四人受伤 ■ 拜登重申美国反对以色列在拉法的行动，除非保护平民 ■ 以色列国防军：数十名恐怖嫌疑人在汗尤尼斯的纳赛尔医院被捕 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：四名纳赛尔医院患者因停电导致氧气供应中断而死亡 ■ 战争开始 133 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 17:56:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-133/0000018d-b2ff-d11b-af9d-b7ffaa130000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称10月7日恐怖分子在汗尤尼斯纳赛尔医院被拘留；哈马斯：患者因停电死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/idf-terrorists-detained-in-khan-yunis-hospital-hamas-patients-died-due-to-power-outage/0000018d-b261-de6d-a1fd-bbe5d1d20000</link><description>以色列军队已经在医院进行手术第三天了。哈马斯管理的加沙卫生部表示，周五早上，四名患者因停电导致医院氧气供应中断而死亡</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 17:04:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/idf-terrorists-detained-in-khan-yunis-hospital-hamas-patients-died-due-to-power-outage/0000018d-b261-de6d-a1fd-bbe5d1d20000</guid></item><item><title>阿巴斯总统的巴勒斯坦建国路线图在加沙被扣押以索取赎金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/president-abbas-roadmap-for-palestinian-statehood-is-held-for-ransom-in-gaza/0000018d-b12c-de6d-a1fd-b9ecc4980000</link><description>随着西方和阿拉伯领导人采取措施建立巴勒斯坦国，年迈的巴勒斯坦总统正试图维持其日渐式微的权力。然而，阿巴斯和以色列都不愿意回答有关未来是什么样子的棘手但必要的问题</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 15:43:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/president-abbas-roadmap-for-palestinian-statehood-is-held-for-ransom-in-gaza/0000018d-b12c-de6d-a1fd-b9ecc4980000</guid></item><item><title>在英国，“反犹太主义和对犹太人的消极态度已成为主流、普遍存在”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-02-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-britain-negative-attitudes-about-jewish-people-have-become-mainstream/0000018d-b1d0-d9b4-a19f-f9d3f9aa0000</link><description>在英国创纪录的反犹太主义袭击一年之后，社区安全信托基金的戴夫·里奇指出，激增是在哈马斯袭击以色列之后立即开始的，而不是在以色列对加沙进行报复期间。</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 13:29:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-02-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-britain-negative-attitudes-about-jewish-people-have-become-mainstream/0000018d-b1d0-d9b4-a19f-f9d3f9aa0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列南部恐怖袭击中枪手造成两人死亡、四人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/two-killed-four-wounded-in-terror-attack-in-southern-israel/0000018d-b1d9-de6d-a1fd-b9dd18c30000</link><description>警方称，枪手驾车抵达十字路口，并向附近的一个公交车站开枪。他被一名开车经过袭击地点的武装平民开枪打死</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 12:27:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/two-killed-four-wounded-in-terror-attack-in-southern-israel/0000018d-b1d9-de6d-a1fd-b9dd18c30000</guid></item><item><title>据报道埃及在加沙边境修建围墙以应对大规模逃亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/egypt-constructing-walled-off-area-on-gaza-border-as-contingency-for-mass-exodus/0000018d-b0f8-de6d-a1fd-b9fcd2920000</link><description>开源情报显示，埃及一直在建设一个坚固的“缓冲区”，一旦加沙人大规模逃往埃及，该缓冲区可以为数万名巴勒斯坦人提供庇护</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 09:15:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/egypt-constructing-walled-off-area-on-gaza-border-as-contingency-for-mass-exodus/0000018d-b0f8-de6d-a1fd-b9fcd2920000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：以色列拒绝国际社会就巴勒斯坦最终地位解决方案发出的命令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israel-rejects-intl-diktats-on-final-status-solution-with-the-palestinians/0000018d-b09b-d070-a7fd-f6bf371c0000</link><description>以色列总理在回应《华盛顿邮报》有关实施两国解决方案计划的报道时表示，单方面承认巴勒斯坦国将是“恐怖活动的巨大奖励”</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 06:44:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israel-rejects-intl-diktats-on-final-status-solution-with-the-palestinians/0000018d-b09b-d070-a7fd-f6bf371c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙南部的战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-in-southern-gaza/0000018d-b08a-de6d-a1fd-b9cee2160000</link><description>参谋军士。哈巴是过去一天在加沙地带战斗中丧生的第二名伞兵</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 06:23:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-in-southern-gaza/0000018d-b08a-de6d-a1fd-b9cee2160000</guid></item><item><title>官员预计以色列和哈马斯将在下个月达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/officials-expect-hostage-deal-between-israel-and-hamas-over-the-next-month/0000018d-ae62-dc8c-a3df-fe772ff80000</link><description>一位参与谈判的消息人士表示，实施协议的“理想时间”是在 3 月 10 日开始的斋月期间</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 04:05:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/officials-expect-hostage-deal-between-israel-and-hamas-over-the-next-month/0000018d-ae62-dc8c-a3df-fe772ff80000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨政党的官员相信内塔尼亚胡已准备好结束紧急政府伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/gantz-party-officials-believe-netanyahu-is-ready-to-end-partnership/0000018d-adda-da6e-af9f-addb2b6a0000</link><description>甘茨领导的民族团结党内的消息人士认为，总理的目标是启动他较为温和的战时内阁伙伴，以强硬反对他的右翼基地的人质交易。一名官员表示，内塔尼亚胡“希望每个人都谈论政治，这样就没有人会谈论人质”</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 04:05:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-16/ty-article/.premium/gantz-party-officials-believe-netanyahu-is-ready-to-end-partnership/0000018d-adda-da6e-af9f-addb2b6a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>